## Key Improvements in Swap Redesign

### Enhanced Security

- Real-time rate validation prevents stale price execution
- Slippage protection prevents unfavorable swaps
- Two-phase execution ensures both parties fulfill obligations

### Improved User Experience

- Configurable slippage tolerance for market volatility
- Clear error messages for failed operations
- Multiple recovery paths for different failure scenarios

### System Efficiency

- Reduced contract complexity with single SwapRequest template
- Streamlined choices for cleaner interaction patterns
- Direction-aware calculations eliminate manual rate selection

### Market Responsiveness

- Current rates validated at time of LP decision
- Flexible slippage tolerance for different market conditions
- Automatic rejection when rates exceed acceptable bounds
